docstrings: * Utility class to calculate difference between 2 sorted lists.

* Creates difference between 2 sorted lists.
     *
     * @param firstList
     *        the first list.
     * @param secondList
     *        the second list.
     * @param <T> the type of elements.
     * @return the difference list.

* Creates difference between 2 non-empty iterators.
     *
     * @param firstIterator
     *        the first iterator.
     * @param secondIterator
     *        the second iterator.
     * @param <T> the type of elements.
     * @return the difference list (always sorted).
